Entertainer and convener #OurMumuDonDo movement, Mr. Charles Oputa, a.k.a Charly Boy, has disclosed the first time he tasted ‘weewee’ — or Indian hemp, what it did to him, and the historical circumstances surrounding his decision. Rating his Indian hemp appetite against those of two Nigerian artistes, the self-proclaimed Area Fada I boasts, “Fela no smoke igbo pass me, Naira Marley na apprentice for weed.” The grandfather entertainer made this known via his Instagram handle on Sunday. See the post: 